original_title: Thru hole I blind/O/Thru hole oui see
overview: Thru hole I blind/O/Thru hole oui see explores the ways that forests are mapped, understood and perceived.  The work draws on rich and diverse knowledge of the New Forest generously made available by a wide array of local specialists and organisations including Forestry England, National Parks Authority and The Verderers of the New Forest. The video is structured like a dream traversing this forest of information.
title: Thru hole I blind/O/Thru hole oui see
